<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
html { background: #ffffff; }
body {
  width: 720pt; height: 405pt; margin: 0; padding: 0;
  background: #F4F6F6;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  display: flex;
}
.header {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 60pt;
  background: #2E4053;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding-left: 40pt;
}
.header h1 {
  color: #FFFFFF;
  font-size: 24pt;
  margin: 0;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.content {
  margin-top: 75pt;
  margin-left: 40pt;
  margin-right: 40pt;
  display: flex;
  gap: 20pt;
}
.section-box {
  background: #FFFFFF;
  border-left: 5pt solid #E67E22;
  padding: 10pt 15pt;
  border-radius: 4pt;
  flex: 1;
}
.section-title {
  color: #E67E22;
  font-size: 13pt;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin: 0 0 8pt 0;
}
.icon-container {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 8pt;
}
.icon-container img {
  width: 40pt;
  height: 40pt;
}
.app-list {
  margin: 0;
  padding-left: 14pt;
}
.app-list li {
  color: #2C3E50;
  font-size: 10pt;
  margin: 2pt 0;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
  <h1>标签打印机 - 台式</h1>
</div>
<div class="content">
  <div class="section-box">
    <p class="section-title">2.5寸</p>
    <div class="icon-container">
      <img src="cafe.png" alt="餐饮">
    </div>
    <ul class="app-list">
      <li>奶茶、鞋服、烘焙价签</li>
      <li>医疗景区腕带等</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section-box">
    <p class="section-title">3寸</p>
    <div class="icon-container">
      <img src="supermarket.png" alt="商超">
    </div>
    <ul class="app-list">
      <li>茶饮、烘焙、商超</li>
      <li>生鲜行业</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section-box">
    <p class="section-title">4寸</p>
    <div class="icon-container">
      <img src="logistics.png" alt="物流">
    </div>
    <ul class="app-list">
      <li>快递仓储面单</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
